      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "0663858D415D37D3FD4CFFA42B82A380",
        "source_text": "触发<#完美闪避>后，短时间内<#普攻><#强化>为<#二技能><#FS1017_S_3>，造成<#流技伤害>。"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "0684C5454AD836D9B49BAABB476CD443",
        "source_text": "施放<#FS1002_S_5>，对目标及其周围敌人造成#power0#<#攻击力>的<#伤害>。"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "079B071143D37289BDA3C3AE46623D2B",
        "source_text": "造成<#伤害>"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "07A72408450E3C0FFD2AF8B390481778",
        "source_text": "造成<#伤害>"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "08071F5D4372D7C4A95380B151C447EB",
        "source_text": "<#普攻>第六段命中或<#完美闪避>后，下一次<#普攻><#强化>为<#FS1017_D_2>。\n发动高速打击，期间连续点按<#普攻>会增加攻击次数。在结束时施放血刺攻击敌人，造成<#普攻伤害>。可以反制敌人<#红光技>。"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "09698502406A0AB7AED8869E8049B13B",
        "source_text": "当前没有刺入<#FS1017_D_3>的敌人时，将<#投掷><#FS1017_D_3>，刺入敌人后可将自身拉向敌人身前，并造成<#普攻伤害>。\n已有刺入<#FS1017_D_3>的敌人时，对其攻击将使<#FS1017_D_3>获得能量，能量充盈时可再次施放。施放时拔出<#FS1017_D_3>，造成<#普攻><#伤害>"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "09699D6542D2C4A19A37F881DFB18DBA",
        "source_text": "施放<#FS1002_S_5>，对目标及其周围敌人造成#power0#<#攻击力>的<#伤害>。"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "099EDB4C4941A0C6C63FD3B63F6780EE",
        "source_text": "进行<Skill_Value>6</>段快速穿梭，每段造成#power0#<#攻击力>的<#伤害>。返回时造成#power1#<#攻击力>的<#伤害>。可以反制怪物红<#光>招式。"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "0B83CE854C3B74356DABEA95E6477511",
        "source_text": "持续发射储备在肩部机关的<#FS1006_D_8>，朝指定方向进行定向轰炸。每发<#FS1006_D_8>对范围内敌人造成#power0#<#攻击力>的范围<#伤害>，共<Skill_Value>24</>发。"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "0BABC2B342F94725BE25DD9AB111CB91",
        "source_text": "造成<#伤害>"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "0CD7F82846DE699B522586A5873282BE",
        "source_text": "触发<#完美闪避>后，短时间内<#普攻><#强化>为<#二技能><#FS1017_S_3>，造成<#流技伤害>。"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "0F8C30B640B04EE86E94858D55B6B26C",
        "source_text": "造成<#伤害>"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "10F3DB1C4303D3EDEB8CB0AF3DE893F0",
        "source_text": "汇聚<#魔道>之力，于目标位置召唤<#FS1011_D_2>。随后召唤莲花法器，莲瓣绽开对拉取范围内敌人造成<#绝技><#伤害>，可以反制敌人<#红光技>。充沛的<#魔道>之力随莲花绽放而被彻底引爆，造成<#绝技><#伤害>，立即将<#FS1011_D_2>持续时间重置为20秒。"
      },
      {
        "namespace": "/Game/Data/DataTables/CombatGrowth/SkillGrowth/DT_SkillGrowthComposite",
        "guid": "12087E144ABD270F479F8590BAAE27C8",
        "source_text": "连续打击附近敌人<Skill_Value>4</>次，每次造成#damage1#<#攻击力>的<#伤害>。"
